        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-453",
        "content": "Scarce, scarce!'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-453_129308_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/453/129308/453_129308_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-453",
        "content": "This brief direction to Charley Bates, and his recent antagonist, was softly and immediately obeyed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-453_129308_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/453/129308/453_129308_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-453",
        "content": "With these words he pulled up the smock frock; and, winding it round his middle, drew a chair to the fire, and placed his feet upon the hob.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
